Package: ir
Title: A Simple Package to Handle and Preprocess Infrared Spectra
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Henning",
           family = "Teickner",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "h_teic01@wwu.de")
Description: 
  Basic functions to import
  and handle infrared spectra (import from .csv and
  Thermo Galactic's .spc, baseline correction, binning, clipping,
  interpolating, smoothing, averaging, plotting).
